## Phase Context
Phase: Phase 1 — Shell, tokens, and auth
What Changes: Dark-mode CSS token system live. Shared shell renders with 9 nav items.
Unlocks Next: Story 1.3 app factory can render real HTML responses.

## Story Context
Story: Story 1.2 — CSS token layer and shared shell
Contributes To: Phase 1 exit state — CSS variables live, shell works.
Unlocks: Story 1.3 can write web.py and login template against known CSS classes.

## Task

### ids/console/static/console.css
All 40 CSS variables from CONTEXT.md Pencil token table (dark values):
  :root { --background:#111111; --foreground:#FFFFFF; --card:#1A1A1A; --card-foreground:#FFFFFF;
    --border:#2E2E2E; --input:#2E2E2E; --muted:#2E2E2E; --muted-foreground:#B8B9B6;
    --primary:#FF8400; --primary-foreground:#111111; --secondary:#2E2E2E; --secondary-foreground:#FFFFFF;
    --accent:#111111; --accent-foreground:#F2F3F0; --destructive:#FF5C33; --ring:#666666;
    --popover:#1A1A1A; --popover-foreground:#FFFFFF;
    --sidebar:#18181b; --sidebar-accent:#2a2a30; --sidebar-accent-foreground:#fafafa;
    --sidebar-foreground:#fafafa; --sidebar-border:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    --sidebar-primary:#18181b; --sidebar-primary-foreground:#fafafa; --sidebar-ring:#71717a;
    --color-success:#222924; --color-success-foreground:#B6FFCE;
    --color-error:#24100B; --color-error-foreground:#FF5C33;
    --color-warning:#291C0F; --color-warning-foreground:#FF8400;
    --color-info:#222229; --color-info-foreground:#B2B2FF;
    --radius-m:16px; --radius-none:0; --radius-pill:999px;
    --font-primary:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; --font-secondary:'Geist',system-ui,sans-serif; }
Plus: shell layout (.shell, .shell__sidebar 280px, .shell__main), sidebar styles, nav-item, topbar, card, btn-primary, body resets.

### ids/console/templates/base.html
<!doctype html> with lang=vi, dark html class, Geist+JetBrains Mono CDN links, console.css, sidebar include when admin, shell__main with topbar+content block, console.js.

### ids/console/templates/partials/app_sidebar.html
280px sidebar: logo (shield + VIGIL IDS), 9 nav items (Overview /overview, Alerts /alerts, Operations /operations, Reports /reports, Live Logs /live-logs, Suppression Rules /suppression-rules, System Health /system-health), user footer with logout form (CSRF).

### ids/console/templates/partials/top_utility_bar.html
.topbar: page_title block + page_actions block.

## Verification
- console.css has all 40 CSS variables with correct dark hex values
- base.html has {% block content %} and {% block title %}
- Sidebar lists all 9 nav items
- Templates are valid Jinja2

## Files In Scope
WRITE: ids/console/static/console.css, ids/console/templates/base.html,
       ids/console/templates/partials/app_sidebar.html, ids/console/templates/partials/top_utility_bar.html
